== History ==
'''Cursed Rage''' is a Chilean multigaming organization, created by the fusion of former [[Cursed Giants]] and [[Inrage Gaming]]. With the strong conviction to make a name in Latin America e-Sports scene, their League of Legends team is the fist of their competitive rosters.

